-- Anglo American Says Bids for Coal Assets in Queensland, NSW Closing Today
-- Elisabeth Behrmann
-- 2010-06-16T01:10:11Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-16/anglo-american-says-bids-for-coal-assets-in-queensland-nsw-closing-today.html

          
          
             Anglo American Plc , which operates
ten mines in Australia, said bids close today for five coal
assets for sale in New South Wales and Queensland states.  
 “The final bids are due in today,” said  Aldo Pennini , a
Brisbane-based regional manager of external affairs, said in a
phone interview. He declined to give details on bidders.  
